snippet.title: SpongeBob SquarePants: The Cosmic Shake | Showcase Trailer 2022
snippet.description:
SpongeBob and his buddy Balloon-Patrick are ready for a new adventure! 

Travel to the Prehistoric Kelp Forest, Wild West Jellyfish Fields and more in this new trailer for SpongeBob SquarePants: The Cosmic Shake! 

SpongeBob SquarePants: The Cosmic Shake is coming to PC, PlayStation 4, Xbox One and Nintendo Switch.
